gtan la dbab|Skt nirṇayaḥ\nEN to establish in; reaching a definitive understanding (RB) , establish, clear-cut decision — [It is very important to establish the unborn nature of the mind.] [ZT, 2006, translator's notes]\nPT estabelecer; chegar a uma compreensão definitiva
