rnam shes brgyad|Skt aṣṭavijñāna, aṣṭau sambhārāḥ\nEN eight consciousnesses, eight gatherings of consciousness — lit. eight gatherings. A way of classifying the functions of the mind according to the Cittamātra school, also used in the Vajrayāna. The eight types of consciousness are the five sense consciousnesses followed by the mental consciousness, the defiled emotional consciousness of conceiving "I," and the consciousness of the ālaya, the fundamental level of the mind. [TPQ, 2010] The consciousnesses of the five senses, the mind consciousness, the emotional consciousness, and the consciousness of the ground of all. [GWPT, 2004][NS] The consciousnesses of the five senses, together with the mind consciousness, defiled mind consciousness, and the consciousness of the ground of all. [OMS, 2018]\nFR huit consciences — Ce sont les consciences visuelle, olfactive, auditive, gustative, tactile et mentale. Quand on en compte huit, on ajoute la conscience émotionnelle (nyon yid kyi rnam shes , skt : kliṣṭamanovijñāna) et la conscience de tréfonds. [CGP, 1997] ce sont les consciences visuelle, olfactive, auditive, gustative, tactile et mentale. Quand on en compte huit, on ajoute la conscience émotionnelle (nyon yid kyi rnam shes), et la conscience de base (kun gzhi’irnam shes). Voir aussi Esprit. [SAYT, 2014] litt. « huit réunions » : classification des fonctions de l'esprit établie par les Cittamâtrins en vigueur dans le Véhicule de Diamant. Il s'agit des cinq consciences sensorielles, du mental souillé qui conçoit le moi et de la conscience fondamentale, ou conscience du fond universel. [Negi] 1. སྦྱིན་པའི་ཚོགས་ dānasambhāraḥ 2. ཚུལ་ཁྲིམས་ཀྱི་ཚོགས་ śīlasambhāraḥ 3. ཐོས་པའི་ཚོགས་ śrutasambhāraḥ 4. ཞི་གནས་ཀྱི་ཚོགས་ śamathasambhāraḥ 5. ལྷག་མཐོང་གི་ཚོགས་ vidarśanāsambhāraḥ 6. བསོད་ནམས་ཀྱི་ཚོགས་ puṇyasambhāraḥ 7. ཡེ་ཤེས་ཀྱི་ཚོགས་ jñānasambhāraḥ 8. སྙིང་རྗེ་ཆེན་པོའི་ཚོགས་ mahākaruṇāsambhāraḥ la.vi.214kha/317. [TDPQ, 2009]\nPT oito consciências — As consciências relativas a cada um dos cinco sentidos, a consciência mental, a consciência emocional e a consciência base ou ālaya.\nES ocho consciencias — Son la seis consciencias más la consciencia emocional y la consciencia subyacente.[PMP, 2002]\nIT otto coscienze — Le sei coscienze più la contaminata coscienza emotiva e la coscienza base di tutto.
